message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product for $14000. This is a high-quality item that I believe would be of great value to you, considering its worth of $12000 to you. I hope we can come to an agreement that satisfies both of us.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product, but I am only able to pay up to $12000 for it. Would you consider accepting this lower price?
